description:
This is a 20 minute workout called '20 Min Gentle Yoga Routine | Beginner Friendly Full Body Stretch' from the channel Charlie Follows.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
